      <title>004-基于RS和GIS提取岸线（一）</title>
      <link href="/2020/07/04/004-ji-yu-rs-he-gis-ti-qu-an-xian-yi/"/>
      <url>/2020/07/04/004-ji-yu-rs-he-gis-ti-qu-an-xian-yi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="基于RS和GIS提取岸线（一）"><a href="#基于RS和GIS提取岸线（一）" class="headerlink" title="基于RS和GIS提取岸线（一）"></a>基于RS和GIS提取岸线（一）</h1><h2 id="一、岸线的定义分类"><a href="#一、岸线的定义分类" class="headerlink" title="一、岸线的定义分类"></a>一、岸线的定义分类</h2><p>​        首先，提取之前必须明确岸线的定义，不然提取完成但定义不清淅也是徒劳。我们平常说的岸线就是海水和陆地的分界线，但是这个定义在科研中显然不够清晰，经过查找相关文献，关于岸线定义（岸线提取方法）有以下几种：</p><h3 id="1-平均潮位法"><a href="#1-平均潮位法" class="headerlink" title="1. 平均潮位法"></a>1. 平均潮位法</h3><blockquote><p>来自郭文</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223552885.png" alt="image-20200704223552885"></p><h4 id="（1）提取瞬时水边线"><a href="#（1）提取瞬时水边线" class="headerlink" title="（1）提取瞬时水边线"></a>（1）提取瞬时水边线</h4><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223600226.png" alt="image-20200704223600226"></p><h4 id="（2）确定一般高潮线"><a href="#（2）确定一般高潮线" class="headerlink" title="（2）确定一般高潮线"></a>（2）确定一般高潮线</h4><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223606246.png" alt="image-20200704223606246"></p><h4 id="（3）确定岸线和陆地的面积"><a href="#（3）确定岸线和陆地的面积" class="headerlink" title="（3）确定岸线和陆地的面积"></a>（3）确定岸线和陆地的面积</h4><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223613588.png" alt="image-20200704223613588"></p><h3 id="2-平均高潮线"><a href="#2-平均高潮线" class="headerlink" title="2. 平均高潮线"></a>2. 平均高潮线</h3><blockquote><p>来自 粟云召</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223621772.png" alt="image-20200704223621772"></p><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223632116.png" alt="image-20200704223632116">)<img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223639223.png" alt="image-20200704223639223"></p><blockquote><p>来自 樊彦国</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223646019.png" alt="image-20200704223646019"></p><blockquote><p>来自 李贺</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223723422.png" alt="image-20200704223723422">)<img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223728315.png" alt="image-20200704223728315"></p><h4 id="潮滩的定义"><a href="#潮滩的定义" class="headerlink" title="潮滩的定义"></a>潮滩的定义</h4><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223742993.png" alt="image-20200704223742993"></p><blockquote><p>来自 王志一</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223751542.png" alt="image-20200704223751542"></p><h3 id="3-瞬时水边线"><a href="#3-瞬时水边线" class="headerlink" title="3. 瞬时水边线"></a>3. 瞬时水边线</h3><blockquote><p>来自 王苗苗</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223756662.png" alt="image-20200704223756662"></p><h3 id="4-最大潮高潮线法"><a href="#4-最大潮高潮线法" class="headerlink" title="4. 最大潮高潮线法"></a>4. 最大潮高潮线法</h3><blockquote><p>来自 魏帆</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/004-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ERS%E5%92%8CGIS%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/image-20200704223803935.png" alt="image-20200704223803935"></p><h2 id="二、目前思路"><a href="#二、目前思路" class="headerlink" title="二、目前思路"></a>二、目前思路</h2><p>结合在ENVI和ARCGIS中实操后，从方便程度和个人能力来说用平均高潮线法进行潮汐纠正是当前能够完成的方法：</p><ol><li><p>通过MNDWI指数提取瞬时水边线（阈值再改改范围范围放大一点）</p></li><li><p>通过非监督分类和监督分类目视解译提取一般高潮线（高、中潮滩之间）</p></li><li><p>瞬时水边线和一般高潮线中线作为岸线（Arcgis怎样实现这一功能）</p></li></ol><hr><p><em>因为本博客浏览量较少，相关论文引用暂时就不用正规格式了。</em></p><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
      
